results = get_compounds('C1=CC2=C(C3=C(C=CC=N3)C=C2)N=C1', 'smiles',
    searchtype='substructure', listkey_count=3)
assert len(results) == 3
for result in results:
    assert all(el in [a['element'] for a in result.atoms] for el in {'C',
        'N', 'H'})
    assert result.heavy_atom_count >= 14
